<!--
    Monochrome silhouette used by FCM + flutter_local_notifications as the
    Android notification small icon. Android requires this to be a fully
    opaque white shape on transparent background so the system can tint it
    with `notification_color`; the colored launcher icon would fall back
    to the generic placeholder bell.

    Shape: stylized "F" sitting in a 24x24dp viewport — matches the brand
    avatar used elsewhere in the app.
-->
